{"tid":2518419,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"Leveraged ETF 討論區","createTime":"2021-05-06T04:23:26.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-06T05:10:11.000Z","uid":71237,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"cbe3368083b5febabfb7b60033aba1b9771a1c51","tid":2518419,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-06T04:23:26.000Z","msg":"受到全倉TQQQ巴打啟發，先開始留意Leveraged ETF依樣嘢。<br />\n所以想開個post大家討論吓。Leveraged ETF係一種極具爭議性嘅產品。無論你支持定係唔支持Leveraged ETF，都歡迎討論。<br />\n<br />\n喺連登比較流行嘅3X ETF：TQQQ、UPRO<br />\n<br />\n參考資料：<br />\n【數學+歷史分析】 Leveraged ETF 可否長揸？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2409324\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2409324</a><br />\n<br />\n對比起UPRO, VOO有咩優勢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2515651\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2515651</a><br />\n<br />\nLeveraged 3X ETF List<br />\n<a href=\"https://etfdb.com/themes/leveraged-3x-etfs/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fetfdb.com%2Fthemes%2Fleveraged-3x-etfs%2F&d=lnSleIYCVJUMUgC9CFuHQtToc6H19M6%2Bti4cloj%2BWDc%3D&h=f68f4d93\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://etfdb.com/themes/leveraged-3x-etfs/</a><br />\n<br />\nLeveraged 2X ETF List<br />\n<a href=\"https://etfdb.com/themes/leveraged-2x-etfs/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fetfdb.com%2Fthemes%2Fleveraged-2x-etfs%2F&d=lnSleIYCVJUMUgC9CFuHQtToc6H19M6%2Bti4cloj%2BWDc%3D&h=eb1a5e44\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://etfdb.com/themes/leveraged-2x-etfs/</a>"},{"pid":"26d4d1654261d68298da38f7cdf86367c0503292","tid":2518419,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-06T04:24:29.000Z","msg":"Leveraged ETF嘅優點缺點都好明顯。<br />\n<br />\n以3X ETF為例。優點係喺underlying連續兩個交易日上升嗰陣，3X ETF嘅升幅會高過underlying嘅升幅3倍。喺underlying連續兩個交易日下跌嗰陣，3X ETF跌幅會少過underlying跌幅3倍。<br />\n<br />\n缺點係當underlying先升後跌或者先跌後升嗰陣，就算underlying價格無變，3X ETF都會輸。假設underlying本身係$100，先升25%後跌20%之後價格會維持不變(100*1.25*0.8 = 100)。<br />\n<br />\n不過如果你揸3X ETF，假設3X ETF本身都係$100。underlying先升25%後跌20%之後，3X ETF就會變成$70 ($100*1.75*0.4)。即使underlying價格不變，3X ETF都會下跌30%。"},{"pid":"1e43a107c1057081c69a44bde4db98e1088e6e0f","tid":2518419,"uid":39643,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-06T04:26:33.000Z","msg":"渣緊soxl<br />\n蝕到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cce3920b4101a1629d9104cf21f3fba9b70e6065","tid":2518419,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-06T04:31:38.000Z","msg":"如果揸3X ETF，當股價一日內下跌超過33.33%，就會直接total loss無翻身機會。<br />\n不過美股有熔斷機制，如果S&amp;P 500跌幅達到20%就會即刻休市。如果你揸UPRO (S&amp;P 500 3X ETF)係唔會出現一日內直接死亡嘅情況。<br />\n<br />\n不過如果你揸嘅唔係UPRO，而係其他Leveraged ETF，發生依種情況嘅機會有幾大就要你自己判斷啦。我自己就揸TQQQ同UPRO，無揸其他Leveraged ETF。"},{"pid":"24195bf91927a01e411701860bacc9b31adfd596","tid":2518419,"uid":89225,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-06T04:49:21.000Z","msg":"以前做開Tqqq TMf +vixm rebalance<br />\n不過而家用ib低息直接做underlying 孖展算。高位慢慢減槓桿<br />\n雖然係同3倍孖展比較 <br />\n但Leverage etf會長期維持3倍每日槓桿。自己做孖展升上去，nav多左 ，loan不變。其實會不停減槓桿。睇進唔進取決定"},{"pid":"ec53a2329514c8d91f4ceaf1624e257d687170df","tid":2518419,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-06T05:02:36.000Z","msg":"TQQQ Summary Prospectus<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.proshares.com/media/prospectus/tqqq_summary_prospectus.pdf?param=1620277203597\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.proshares.com%2Fmedia%2Fprospectus%2Ftqqq_summary_prospectus.pdf%3Fparam%3D1620277203597&d=lnSleIYCVJUMUgC9CFuHQtToc6H19M6%2Bti4cloj%2BWDc%3D&h=ce6e699f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.proshares.com/media/prospectus/tqqq_summary_prospectus.pdf?param=1620277203597</a><br />\n<br />\nUPRO Summary Prospectus<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.proshares.com/media/prospectus/upro_summary_prospectus.pdf?param=1620277306266\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.proshares.com%2Fmedia%2Fprospectus%2Fupro_summary_prospectus.pdf%3Fparam%3D1620277306266&d=lnSleIYCVJUMUgC9CFuHQtToc6H19M6%2Bti4cloj%2BWDc%3D&h=54b90101\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.proshares.com/media/prospectus/upro_summary_prospectus.pdf?param=1620277306266</a>"},{"pid":"1ccd8c13ea2572c06b411743675bd50f1445df34","tid":2518419,"uid":198783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-06T05:08:40.000Z","msg":"SOXL <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b48181c30b1942e2d4f1184d59a6b8ca2d78ad90","tid":2518419,"uid":2625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-06T05:10:11.000Z","msg":"Lm"}]}